stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> IDLE
  IDLE --> ARMED: classify
  ARMED --> LIVE: Dispatch click
  LIVE --> COMPLETE: all agents OK
  LIVE --> FAILED: any agent FAIL
  LIVE --> CANCELLED: operator CANCEL
  COMPLETE --> RESULTS_VISIBLE: artifacts persisted
  RESULTS_VISIBLE --> [*]
  FAILED --> RESULTS_VISIBLE: partial artifacts
  CANCELLED --> [*]
